A service provided by Argentina-based IT company PRO-Systems that acts as a direct buyer of Bitcoins.  Clients sell their Bitcoins anonymously by transferring them to an address received when placing an order.  Once the Bitcoin transaction is confirmed the money is sent to the specified PayPal account.

The service was launched on Oct 14, 2012.

